{"id":76942,"title":"Managing hyperlipidemia. The updated cholesterol treatment guidelines.","abstract":": The ACC/AHA 2013 cholesterol treatment guidelines focus on lowering the risk of heart disease and stroke and not on targeted treatment goals in adult patients. This article offers a synopsis of the new guidelines and how to apply them in clinical practice. ","date":"2014-06-17","categories":"Nutritional and Metabolic Diseases","split":"train","url":"http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/24878833","annotations":[{"name":"Cholesterol","weight":0.804766,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cholesterol"},{"name":"Heart disease","weight":0.78464,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heart_disease"},{"name":"Disease","weight":0.705743,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Disease"},{"name":"Stroke","weight":0.689375,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stroke"},{"name":"Heart","weight":0.669249,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Heart"},{"name":"Therapy","weight":0.442761,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Therapy"},{"name":"Hyperlipidemia","weight":0.441591,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hyperlipidemia"},{"name":"Risk","weight":0.281557,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Risk"},{"name":"Adult","weight":0.240107,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adult"},{"name":"Targeted therapy","weight":0.131186,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Targeted_therapy"},{"name":"Clinical psychology","weight":0.0177991,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Clinical_psychology"},{"name":"2013","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/2013"},{"name":"Treatment Guidelines from The Medical Letter","weight":0.0168623,"wikipedia_article":"http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Treatment_Guidelines_from_The_Medical_Letter"}]}
